Package com.ee364project

package com.ee364project
Package com.ee364project contains classes related to the EE364 project. It represents a simulation of a company's call center. There are classes for simulation of a Customer, Agent, Problem, Call. Utilities are in the Utilities class in the helpers package.
Author:
Team 2
